A SCHOOL PROGRAM PROVIDES FRESH

12:36.255 --> 12:37.924
VEGETABLES AND OTHER STAPLES

12:37.924 --> 12:40.593
MEANT ONLY FOR THE CHILDREN.

12:40.593 --> 12:42.195
BUT THE FREE FOOD ATTRACTS A

12:42.195 --> 12:44.664
VISITOR: THEIR FATHER.

13:27.507 --> 13:28.141
>> Reporter: DESPITE THE

13:28.141 --> 13:31.611
HARDSHIP, JOAB STAYS IN SCHOOL.

13:31.611 --> 13:33.312
MRS. ASEGO KEEPS CLOSE TRACK OF

13:33.312 --> 13:35.481
HIM, INVOLVING HIM IN POETRY

13:35.481 --> 13:37.183
PERFORMANCE COMPETITIONS TO KEEP

13:37.183 --> 13:38.484
HIM MOTIVATED.

