LATE, HE'S AN INDEPENDENT-MINDED

13:57.503 --> 13:59.672
18-YEAR OLD, ENTERING NINTH

13:59.672 --> 14:00.773
GRADE.

14:00.773 --> 14:01.708
AND THAT'S NOT AN EASY

14:01.708 --> 14:03.176
TRANSITION.

14:03.176 --> 14:04.210
>> HERE IN SCHOOL THERE ARE

14:04.210 --> 14:05.878
RULES AND REGULATIONS.

