MUSEUM FEATURED CLASSIC KATZ.

19:00.106 --> 19:01.540
GROUP PORTRAITS

19:01.540 --> 19:02.641
BRIGHT COLORS.

19:02.641 --> 19:04.143
CLEAN LINES.

19:04.143 --> 19:05.511
AND HIS MAIN SUBJECT OF RECENT

19:05.511 --> 19:07.146
YEARS: LANDSCAPES.

19:07.146 --> 19:08.314
HIS INSPIRATION COMES FROM

19:08.314 --> 19:11.283
OBSERVATION.

19:11.283 --> 19:12.385
LIKE A WALLFLOWER, PAINTING

19:12.385 --> 19:13.085
FAMILY AND FRIENDS AND OTHER

19:13.085 --> 19:15.121
PEOPLE HE MEETS.

