>> YEAH, I'VE ASKED WAITERS,

19:16.489 --> 19:17.556
WAITRESSES TO POSE.

19:17.556 --> 19:18.357
YOU KNOW, THEY THINK I'M COMING

19:18.357 --> 19:22.261
ON.

