AND SOMEONE TELLS THEM, "OH NO.

19:23.029 --> 19:25.498
HE'S A REALLY GOOD PAINTER."

19:25.498 --> 19:27.099
>> Reporter: HIS FAVORITE

19:27.099 --> 19:29.035
SUBJECT ACROSS THE DECADES HAS

19:29.035 --> 19:30.403
BEEN HIS WIFE, ADA, PAINTING HER

19:30.403 --> 19:32.371
MORE THAN 250 TIMES.

