AND I THOUGHT THE COLOR AROUND

20:33.566 --> 20:34.600
HERE, YOU KNOW, IS JUST REALLY

20:34.600 --> 20:36.836
MARVELOUS.

20:36.836 --> 20:37.536
AND THAT WAS A BIG REASON FOR

20:37.536 --> 20:39.171
COMING HERE.

20:39.171 --> 20:40.539
>> Reporter: HE'S COME BACK TO

20:40.539 --> 20:41.841
COASTAL MAINE FOR THE PAST 61

20:41.841 --> 20:43.309
SUMMERS.

